Description
1. Work with food production in different stages cooking, mixing, molding of decoration pieces.
2. Folding of boxes to contain cakes.
3. Slicing of cake sponge.
4. Area cleaning including cleaning of food machines as and when assigned
Requirement
1. No experience required but willing to learn and accept different job functions in production department
2. Understanding of health and safety regulations
3. Good teamwork and able to work independently
4. Able to stand for long periods of time and willing to work overtime
5. Work in aircondition environment
6. Willing to enter coldroom with warm clothing for stock check, issue and storage
8. Part-time applicant should state their time availability/ day plus asking hourly pay for consideration